Bioses.Name: BY99RD25 BIOS for Huananzhi X99-TF Republic of Belarus Edition
Bioses.Description:
After flashing this BIOS you will not be able to use Flash Programming Tool (FPT) any more.
This BIOS has problems with legacy boot, UEFI works well.
⚠️ Some early samples of Huananzhi X99-TF have defective BIOS chips which are too small for this BIOS.
